fts that need work, not the files I thought were done. So the file listing shows Section 10 with substantial content, but the actual Section 7 file ends with placeholder stubs for Sections 8, 9, and 10 instead of including them as separate files. This suggests either those placeholders reference separate files I haven't located, or they were added as a reminder that those sections still need to be written. The file sizes also seem off—a combined Section 7 file with all that content plus placeholders would be much larger than 178 lines. Let me actually look at what's physically at the end of that file to understand the real structure.\n","thinkingSignature":"28d2e31a4c6042010198bd3342bab15da894a5d6b0d5f46c4405923fd1829e1f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_je3jujye9ltq_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":160,"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-7-Your-First-Automation.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":681,"output":1058,"cacheRead":62016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63755,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777652514036,"responseId":"064406225a350221fea6501e754a00d5"}}
