{"type":"message","id":"b014ce9c","parentId":"a149f2e8","timestamp":"2026-05-01T16:26:02.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Port 8790 worked. Now let me tell Bobby about it.\n","thinkingSignature":"f9b1888429aa405a1f82bd65bf26bde37fa8bbd39e688a64f9390749ad880da7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHere's what I found:\n\n**You're right — Sections 7 through 10 aren't fully written.** They're shells with draft intros but the meat of the content is placeholders. Here's the breakdown:\n\n| Section | Status |\n|---------|--------|\n| 1–6 | ✅ Complete |\n| 7 | ✅ First half done, ends with 3 placeholder stubs (Voice Memo, Q&A, My Daily Workflow) |\n| 8 | ⚠️ Shell — no real content |\n| 9 | ⚠️ Shell — no real content |\n| 10 | ✅ Fully written |\n\n---\n\n**The questionnaire is ready.** I built a local web form you can fill out and submit. Here's how to access it:\n\n👉 **http://localhost:8790/questionnaire.html**\n\nIt asks about:\n- Guide title and target audience\n- Your author bio / intro blurb\n- Tone (casual, confident, motivational, chill)\n- What the conclusion / next steps should say\n- Topics to add or cut\n- Cover page style (simple, detailed, bold)\n- Whether to show $9 on the cover\n- Where you want to sell it\n\nOnce you submit it, it'll send the answers straight to me and I'll finish the guide.\n\n**Priority order I'll tackle once you fill it out:**\n1. Write full content for Sections 7 (remaining), 8, and 9\n2. Update intro/author bio based on your answers\n3. Add a proper conclusion section\n4. Generate the final PDF\n\nFill out the form whenever you're ready — no rush. Want me to open it for you?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":161,"output":345,"cacheRead":67072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67578,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777652745548,"responseId":"0644070987e99c79152b0d8a2f8c6906"}