{"type":"message","id":"0ab0d449","parentId":"31d8f1e7","timestamp":"2026-05-01T18:12:35.513Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to make sure I build exactly what he wants before I start. Let me think about what clarifications I need:\n\n1. **Browser choice** — Chrome or Safari? He uses Chrome for automation but Safari has better native speech recognition on Mac\n2. **Where should the audio play?** Through speakers? Headphones?\n3. **Should the transcribed text show on screen while he's talking?**\n4. **What should the page look like?** Minimal? Dark mode like the questionnaire?\n5. **Should it be full screen or just a small window?**\n6. **What happens after I respond — does it loop back to listening or does he have to press again?**\n7. **Should there be a \"stop\" button or just press-and-hold?**\n\n\n8. **Does it need to show my text response on screen too, or just the audio reply?**\n9. **Should the page live at localhost or somewhere else?**\n\nI should keep this concise and just ask the key questions.\n","thinkingSignature":"e380b74d7972a3ddc4a195f60bdc89952923ae82d0f9be1a8e87145b687409da"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nA few quick things before I build:\n\n1. **Browser** — Chrome or Safari?\n2. **Press-and-hold mic** or **toggle on/off**?\n3. **Show my text response** on screen while audio plays, or just audio?\n4. **Loop back to listening automatically** after you hear my reply, or tap to start again?\n5. **Dark or light page?**\n6. **Where to put it** — same folder as the questionnaire?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":81562,"output":304,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81994,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777659148056,"responseId":"0644200cf1f40f1d64b31f701effc083"}}
