{"type":"message","id":"15135f3c","parentId":"ce53f829","timestamp":"2026-05-01T19:24:22.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me also send a text message with the link.\n","thinkingSignature":"598bfeb4cf5836f9adfa7b58afd8e43cde35b8c8a1f53f256215d0e64d937c5b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n**Telephone is ready.** Open it in Safari:\n\n[http://192.168.1.162:8790/telephone.html](http://192.168.1.162:8790/telephone.html)\n\n**What's running:**\n- Server on port 8791\n- Dean listening in background (dean.js)\n- Fairy lights canvas with 4 modes — idle, listening (you), thinking, replying\n\n**To use:** Tap the mic button, talk, release. Dean hears it, thinks, replies with voice. Tap again.\n\nTell me if anything needs adjusting — fairy light behavior, mic sensitivity, response speed, anything."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":159,"output":144,"cacheRead":97088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97391,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777663457243,"responseId":"064430e1b758c625655db6f05acadae1"}}
