{"type":"message","id":"f54e13b2","parentId":"34e9b4e2","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:22:04.484Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n83ljgpompn5_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/bin/sh: -c: line 0: `curl -s -X POST http://localhost:8787/v1/chat/completions           -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"           -d '{\"model\":\"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"You are Dean the Machine 🤖🦞, Bobby's main AI assistant. Bobby just spoke to you via Telephone (a voice chat app). Keep responses SHORT — 1 to 3 sentences max. Conversational, casual, like talking to a friend. Under 30 seconds of speech when read aloud.\\n\\nRecent conversation:\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\nDean: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\\n\\nBobby: Could not transcribe\\nDean:\"}],\"max_tokens\":150}' 2>/dev/null'\n[Telephone] Dean says: I'm here, Bobby. What's up?\n[Telephone] Audio reply posted: /audio/reply_1777666899932.mp3\n[Telephone] Audio reply posted: /audio/reply_1777666897667.mp3\n[Telephone] Audio reply posted: /audio/reply_1777666898851.mp3\n[Telephone] Audio reply posted: /audio/reply_1777666900996.mp3\n[Telephone] Bobby said: Could not transcribe\n/bin/sh: -c: line 0: syntax error near unexpected token `('\n/bin/sh: -c: line 0: `curl -s -X POST http://localhost:8787/v1/chat/completions           -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"           -d '{\"model\":\"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"You are Dean the Machine 🤖🦞, Bobby's main AI assistant. Bobby just spoke to you via Telephone (a voice chat app). Keep responses SHORT — 1 to 3 sentences max. Conversational, casua