{"type":"message","id":"b763145d","parentId":"2a8cec21","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:27:51.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, but the TOOLS.md says the gateway is on port 8787. Let me check the actual config again.\n\nActually looking at it more carefully - the `gateway.port` is 18789. But `lsof` shows the gateway is on port 18789. However, earlier when I checked TOOLS.md it said port 18789. So the gateway is on 18789, not 8787.\n\nBut wait - the lsof output also showed port 8787 is taken by mission-control-api.cjs. So 8787 is the mission control API server.\n\nLet me update the TOOLS.md to reflect the correct gateway port.\n\nActually, let me also fix the dean.js to use port 18789 and restart the services.","thinkingSignature":"bccd19152a38c6f1e2b4b8fd215ef5c6cdf0ec83450f983de0d42febbd101d72"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gw4r4ghquj9s_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Fix port in dean.js and restart\npkill -f \"dean.js\" 2>/dev/null\nsleep 1\ncd ~/Desktop/Telephone && node dean.js > ~/.openclaw/logs/telephone-dean.log 2>&1 &\nsleep 2\n\n# Test AI call with correct port\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:18789/v1/chat/completions \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer test\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Say hello to Bobby\"}],\"max_tokens\":50}' 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":136,"output":330,"cacheRead":102880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103346,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777667268866,"responseId":"06443fc45e3d44577cf8b16d4fc065ad"}}
