{"type":"message","id":"bc149d2e","parentId":"0f91d6fe","timestamp":"2026-05-01T20:28:13.100Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The prod-server proxies `/tools/` to `GATEWAY_PORT` which is 18789. So the path is `/tools/` not `/v1/chat/completions`.\n\nLet me check what the GATEWAY_PORT paths look like:\n- `/tools/*` → proxied to 18789\n- `/api/*` → proxied to 3001\n- Static files from `dist/`\n\nAnd the OpenClaw Gateway at 18789 has its own API paths. Let me test:\n","thinkingSignature":"8c1c4cd058219c03f1231b894db84aad467b6bf1879cb54ff3bb568a196a1688"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f4lricfvjjil_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test the correct path through the proxy\ncurl -s -X POST \"http://localhost:8787/tools/v1/chat/completions\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Say hello to Bobby\"}],\"max_tokens\":50}' 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":141,"output":216,"cacheRead":104768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105125,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777667291220,"responseId":"06443fdbf185e90a5d335585d37c04dc"}}
